data.description: Motivated Seller, Make us an offer!! Great northwest side home in established Heritage Farms community.  Home sits on almost a quarter acre. (4) bedrooms, (2) remodeled baths, master bath has large stand up shower with seat, tiled living area. 2 car garage with garage door opener. Stone surround wood burning fireplace in living room, open floor plan kitchen, dining, living areas. Stainless steel Appliances convey. Large covered back patio for entertaining in a quiet cul-de-sac. Wood floors in some of the secondary bedrooms. Ceiling fans in bedrooms and living room. Walking distance to duck pond where you can feed the ducks, go on the walking trail or for a swim in the community pool.  Minutes from Lackland AFB, SeaWorld, dining and entertainment. Home warranty to be included. Open House on Saturday, Dec 9th from 1:00 - 4:00!!
